Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.99,0:01:36.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我瞞著大家能看見妖怪的事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.69,0:01:40.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  傘飛起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.21,0:01:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傘？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.43,0:01:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.55,0:01:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啦  就在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.24,0:01:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏啊  哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.95,0:01:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裏  哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.42,0:01:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  大概看錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.61,0:01:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.22,0:01:59.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.76,0:02:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.79,0:02:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能看見我嗎  人類
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:19.78,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(860,260)\fs80}淺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:19.78,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(860,500)\fs80}蔥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:19.78,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(588,510)\fs80}{\c&H0025000}的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.78,0:02:19.78,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(330,525)\fs80}琴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.34,0:02:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不想碰人類  迫不得已了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:33.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身體我要了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.33,0:02:35.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:37.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.81,0:02:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.51,0:02:55.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真沒耐性
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:00.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是鈣 吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.62,0:03:03.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.09,0:03:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  我竟會…明明是人類還挺能幹的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:13.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好  不管了  這個身體我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.90,0:03:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  銅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:20.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類啊  請原諒他的無禮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.83,0:03:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這全是為了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:25.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葫蘆裏傳出了聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺蔥  別說話  會累的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.79,0:03:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.02,0:03:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.30,0:03:48.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺蔥  我聽過這名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高貴的妖怪們聚集的幻之裏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.97,0:03:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}畿{\r}月森林裏有一位美麗的蒼琴師叫「淺蔥」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那個淺蔥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:07.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  但她身體抱恙以至無法繼續彈琴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被送回了故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.78,0:04:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是面帶笑容的人  完全沒了精神
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.23,0:04:20.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以人類的孩子啊  為了淺蔥你暫時將身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:26.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不聽話我就咬掉你的耳朵或鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.85,0:04:28.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我住手  低級的  他是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:34.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被貍貓咬了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說啥！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.20,0:04:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許笑  地藏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.24,0:04:42.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕易接近妖怪肯定沒好事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何況還要我借出身體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是面帶笑容的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:54.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我覺得有點可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:10.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早  貓咪老師
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:12.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是早上才回來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  你的頭髮…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:22.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛的顏色好像也變藍了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.04,0:05:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪  變回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.86,0:05:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是錯覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.72,0:05:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  早啊  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  早安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:48.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…早  北本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.90,0:05:52.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇…嚇我一跳  一瞬間還以為認錯了人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:54.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  這兩人在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:53.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:05:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的辭典
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:03.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫了大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:06.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:12.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  掉了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.20,0:06:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  田沼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,田沼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  一瞬間把夏目看成女人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:34.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  是我的錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:38.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.62,0:06:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說北本  田沼感覺到什麼的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.78,0:06:45.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.06,0:07:01.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁你睡覺時讓淺蔥進入了你的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.20,0:07:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像同化得很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  暫時請你合作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晨的藍色頭髮和眼睛就是附身現象嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.90,0:07:22.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我叫他別這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.71,0:07:26.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但無法阻止  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.49,0:07:29.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個聲音…你就是淺蔥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要責備他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.40,0:07:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是我不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  你不用道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:42.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.11,0:07:48.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她從你身體裏出來的方法？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.28,0:07:50.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了強行驅逐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就只能去實現淺蔥的願望了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:58.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願望得到滿足就會自然離開你的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.96,0:08:01.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但她的願望…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.45,0:08:07.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光說也沒用  趕快實現願望讓我們回去吧  人類
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:09.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪不到你說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從哪來的  叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:15.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有講給人類聽的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.96,0:08:18.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你現在起就叫蛇眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.77,0:08:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇眼傘的蛇眼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:22.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇眼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.43,0:08:25.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來接我們辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:27.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這貍貓…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.72,0:08:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛的名字  太好了呢  蛇眼先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺蔥  怎麼連你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.40,0:08:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好啊  不是很開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺蔥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.52,0:08:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.88,0:08:47.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才身體被佔領了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心就…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.51,0:08:53.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:57.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫你的  彈了琴就會離開我的身體了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:08:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.42,0:09:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  要從製作琴開始？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:06.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  因為是特別的琴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種額頭上有白線  跟鯉魚長得一樣  叫拉絲的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要抓住這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:16.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要抓魚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:22.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？少廢話  別擺出副鬱悶的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:24.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:38.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:41.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.12,0:09:41.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.79,0:09:42.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:48.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺蔥和蛇眼是什麼關係啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.02,0:09:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.82,0:10:00.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會  蛇眼是負責撐傘的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撐傘？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:10.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}畿{\r}月森林聚集了主人壬生大人看上的有才之人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裏為壬生大人和大家撐傘  並保護他們是蛇眼的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:25.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇眼很能幹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.46,0:10:43.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}畿{\r}月像夢境一般美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.52,0:10:49.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想永遠留在那裏  一直待在壬生大人身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.37,0:10:54.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠  永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.71,0:11:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不能彈琴了就趕出來  真是心胸狹窄的神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:04.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:09.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是壬生大人收留了無處可去的我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:14.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了自己沒用  我離開了那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了  這就是拉絲  怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:28.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  這就是要用來做琴弦的線
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:32.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那材料收集就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.53,0:11:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  接下來是琴身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.70,0:11:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找樹墩  而且上面要長著剛發芽的竹筍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再等一下  再等一下就能讓你彈琴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.59,0:12:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇眼真的對淺蔥…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:11.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  怎麼了  全身濕成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:13.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛巾毛巾
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  貴志會感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.76,0:12:18.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:26.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看  好好擦乾  真的都濕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.07,0:12:31.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想永遠留在那裏  永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:35.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.10,0:12:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好剛空出來  快去洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.67,0:12:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能在這裏待到什麼時候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.24,0:13:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是…夢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.59,0:13:18.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是淺蔥的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:21.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.35,0:13:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵醒你了嗎  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.31,0:13:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  淺蔥她睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.64,0:13:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果想跟她說話的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺蔥的手指已經不能彈琴了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.44,0:13:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體像乾枯的泥土一樣剝落的病
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:38.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經無法挽回了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.51,0:13:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但進入別的容器時惡化會變慢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.47,0:13:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後一次看到她笑是在壬生大人面前彈琴  一臉幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.78,0:13:56.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在演奏中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皮膚突然開始剝落
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪白修長的手指和發光的臉頰…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在憧憬不已的壬生大人面前…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天是滿月  通往{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}畿{\r}月的路會打開一會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.49,0:14:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想最後讓她在壬生大人面前彈一次琴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.05,0:14:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之前請讓她借用你的力量  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛇眼為什麼…為什麼這麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.95,0:14:47.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  銅
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.02,0:14:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是個撐傘的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:02.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  怎麼都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.92,0:15:05.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  在哪裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.36,0:15:06.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏真的有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在找什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.42,0:15:22.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長竹子的樹墩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在催情草的草叢中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.14,0:15:29.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的  有了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.37,0:15:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我跟什麼說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.19,0:15:33.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.54,0:15:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告訴你了哦  作為交換我要拿走你的腸子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:43.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了  跟奇怪的妖怪說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  夏目  你在好好地找嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了不起  夏目  就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.89,0:15:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  趕快動手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.95,0:16:11.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體開始不舒服了  這種無力有點發熱的感覺是淺蔥的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼弱的身體還去演奏  淺蔥的生命會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:23.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  真對不起  都是因為我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:27.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來我都沒確認過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.62,0:16:28.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.54,0:16:32.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺蔥你想彈琴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.94,0:16:34.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能再次…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.69,0:16:40.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果還有一次機會  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.37,0:16:47.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不靈巧  手指僵硬可能彈不好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.47,0:16:48.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺蔥  你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銅他一直  一直對你…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.62,0:17:19.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.92,0:17:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  還來得及
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:26.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銅  怎麼了  到底要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:35.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淺蔥  現在通往{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}畿{\r}月的路還開放著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.37,0:17:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去吧  然後為壬生大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.41,0:17:40.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:43.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約好的  我來取你的腸子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.63,0:17:45.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:54.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.96,0:18:09.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴  淺蔥和蛇眼重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.22,0:18:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.18,0:18:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:24.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.64,0:18:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:28.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把那傢伙趕走了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.59,0:18:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:33.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  多虧你的保護
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:36.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:41.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起來嗎  現在還能趕得上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.49,0:18:43.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的話我來抱你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是蛇眼  受了這樣的傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.99,0:18:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.24,0:18:52.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:03.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能彈我想再彈一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.96,0:19:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直只為那位大人彈著琴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以如果能再彈一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:22.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要為了溫柔的  我重要的朋友你彈一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.78,0:19:27.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,銅  你能聽我彈琴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:48.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從遠處聽到了音樂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:53.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從未聽見過的美麗音符
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:20:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音符從我的指尖流出  劃開空氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.79,0:20:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像降落到空中一般  淺蔥離開了我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.81,0:20:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.61,0:20:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.62,0:20:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶淺蔥回故鄉去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.26,0:20:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.88,0:20:48.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是睡得很深很沉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  再見了  淺蔥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.20,0:20:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了  蛇眼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:09.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪裏了啊  老師  在人家辛苦的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服了嗎  你這個爛好人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.81,0:21:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了  去給我買包子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:17.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七{\fe128\fscx80\fscy92\fnDFPTFLeiSho-W5}辻{\r}屋還沒開門哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.31,0:21:18.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.18,0:21:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓咪老師有過想永遠待下去的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.93,0:21:27.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種地方我一輩子都不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.70,0:21:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.77,0:21:35.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來一直這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.55,0:21:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  別抱我  放開  還不放開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.31,0:21:42.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我試著彈了留下的琴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:46.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那美麗的音符不再出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那音符不是出自我的手指  是出自她的心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.11,0:21:55.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃早飯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.68,0:21:56.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.07,0:23:51.09,biaoti1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(140,550)}貓咪徒然帳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.46,0:23:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  老師  你幹了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.75,0:23:40.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幹這種事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.44,0:23:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別裝傻了  給我出去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.98,0:23:44.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  我出去  夏目這個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.68,0:23:46.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我掉進了洞裏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.82,0:23:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  天上掉下只白色小豬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

